text: Thank you to New Orleans Area American Heart Association and Entergy's The Power to Care for putting together the "STEM goes Red" conference for our 9th - 12th-grade girls. The students were empowered by STEM-related professionals to explore careers in those fields. They had a full day of hands-on activities, talking to professionals, and had the chance to view Xavier University of Louisiana campus. #EinsteinSTRONG #STRONGerTogether #stemgoesred #NOLAgoesred
